department store in Jiang City,

247
00:12:24,540 --> 00:12:25,220
Zhang Qianli.

248
00:12:25,610 --> 00:12:26,300
Nice to meet you.

249
00:12:29,340 --> 00:12:30,620
I've come with sincerity.

250
00:12:31,980 --> 00:12:32,660
Mr. Laurent,

251
00:12:32,780 --> 00:12:33,990
the perfume you're looking for

252
