269
00:13:17,580 --> 00:13:18,820
You have one thousand bottles?

270
00:13:18,940 --> 00:13:19,710
All in stock

271
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,140
and ready for delivery at any time.

272
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:21,980
That's great.

273
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:22,720
I'll take them all.

274
00:13:22,730 --> 00:13:24,300
Thank you for trusting me, Mr. Laurent.

275
00:13:24,300 --> 00:13:25,700
