282
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:44,420
However,

283
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:45,980
it's no small amount.

284
00:13:46,540 --> 00:13:47,260
Mr. Laurent,

285
00:13:47,580 --> 00:13:48,220
please give us

286
00:13:48,460 --> 00:13:49,380
